{"type": "article", "id": 16969, "title": "New Mexico", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-03T06:00:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114957GWuU74ZMPArShbqQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以色列设计师 Nir Meiri 擅长做有特殊意义的灯具，他在伦敦设计节上带来的这个系列就有环保意义。他使用了普通商店就能买到的陶罐，用车床加工的木质零件和 3D 打印的细部零件，既可以用来做放植物的陶罐，也可以做吊灯、桌灯和喇叭，有一种质朴的手工感，很居家。<a href=\"http://www.nirmeiri.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144209wFZBycVDUAva7kRl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144210ZXbjvotmdeBR2LuD.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"511\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144211JrfXAUSCkxq32ymT.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261442111Uy6WGhjZStn4lsB.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"412\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144212HOg9MkIDiqAUhT1v.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"485\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}